title: 257.066 RULES.
text: By December 31, 1989, the commissioner of children, youth, and families shall revise Minnesota Rules, parts 9545.0750 to 9545.0830, 9560.0010 to 9560.0180, and 9560.0500 to 9560.0670 to ensure that, as conditions of licensure, social services and child-placing agencies meet the requirements of section 260C.215, subdivisions 6 and 7, and keep records in compliance with sections 257.01 and 259.79.
